hiawatha (12.0-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add debian/hiawatha.init — LSB-compliant SysV init script for
    compatibility with sysvinit and OpenRC-based systems (Devuan, etc.).
    dh_installinit handles permissions and update-rc.d integration
    automatically via debhelper compat 13.

 -- Chris Wadge <cwadge@tuxhelp.org>  Fri, 04 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0000

hiawatha (12.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add debian/hiawatha.service — upstream CMakeLists.txt does not install
    a systemd unit file; provide one as a packaging overlay so that the
    service can be managed via systemctl after installation.

 -- Chris Wadge <cwadge@tuxhelp.org>  Fri, 04 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000

